content: What strategies work best for Alex?
Based on Alex's profile, visual schedules and fidget tools have been most effective. Alex responds well to advance warnings before transitions and benefits from social stories for new situations.
Jordan's main triggers include long sitting periods, transitions between activities, and waiting. Movement breaks and hands-on activities help manage these triggers effectively.
